Game setup
both Player 1 & 2 have 3 lives each
game continues until either one player has no life remain


Game mechanics - loop
question is asked
take answer from Player 1 
  if correct, update score: win value
  else, take a life away from Player 1
    update score& life remain & outputs
question is asked
take anser from Player 2
  if correct, update score: win value
  else, take a life away from Player 1
    update score& life remain & outputs
    
Game initialization
initialize Players' win & lives remain
